648
00:39:22,480 --> 00:39:23,160
Qin Gang.

649
00:39:32,160 --> 00:39:33,220
What are you doing?

650
00:39:34,680 --> 00:39:36,940
I want to go in and apologize to your aunt.

651
00:39:37,040 --> 00:39:38,520
If she sees you now,

652
00:39:38,520 --> 00:39:40,450
